Contact
Dante's Key West
2022-01-14T15:14:32+00:00
CONTACT US TODAY
Dante’s Key West
We are located at 951 Caroline Street in the Conch Harbor Plaza. The nearest cross street is Grinnell.
Address:
951 Caroline St. Key West, FL 33040
Phone:
305-293-5123
Email:
info@danteskeywest.com
Hours:
Lunch is served from 11AM – 6PM
Dinner is served from 5:30PM – 10PM
Please see below for map & directions as well as Frequently Asked Questions.
There are multiple points of entry.
From the boardwalk in the historic seaport:
In between the Key West Ferry Terminal and Half Shell Raw Bar
From the parking lot in between Turtle Kraal’s and the Half Shell:
Just walk across the lot.
From Caroline Street: Behind the West Marine
From the Conch Harbor Plaza Parking Garage: Located at the end of Grinnell Street at Caroline. Parking available for: $5/hr or $35 for 24 hour period
DANTE’S KEY WEST
Frequently Asked Questions
Bachelor & Bachelorette Parties
While we do not accept reservations, here are some tips that may be useful:
If you’re looking for a poolside table or lounge chairs(the hot spots), we recommend arriving at around opening at 11am.
If you want to sleep in a bit, there will still be plenty of other seating available and servers to bring you all the food and drink you desire wherever you sit!
The DJ is happy to make special announcements for you, just chat with them when you arrive for the day!
Where Are You Located?
We are located at 951 Caroline Street in the Conch Harbor Plaza. The nearest cross street is Grinnell.
Do We Need To Make Reservations?
No, we do not take reservations. However, if you have a group of 30 or more, please contact us at 305-293-5123 or at
info@danteskeywest.com
Is There A Cover Charge?
There is no cover charge. All you have to do is actively eat & drink while you are here!
What Time Does Dante’s Open?
Dante’s Pool & Restaurant opens every day at 11AM and is open until 10PM.
Lunch is served from 11AM – 6PM
Dinner is served from 5:30PM – 10PM
Lunch specials every day 11am-3pm.
Check out our daily lunch specials on our Facebook page.
Here’s some info that may be useful:
If you’re looking to snag a poolside umbrella table or chaise lounges, we recommend arriving at or near opening at 11 AM. If that’s not important to you there will still be plenty of other seating available later in the day with servers to bring you all of your food and drinks wherever you land. The DJ starts at noon and plays until six (5pm in the winter)….. they’re happy to make any announcements for you just swing by the DJ tent that day.

About Us
Live bands and DJ’s provide the soundtrack as bartenders prepare over-FUELed drinks and the kitchen turns the bounty of our local waters into mouth-watering delights! Stone crabs, lobster, oysters and always the freshest local fish, transformed into tacos, po’ boys and platters.
Prime Steakhouse
Visit
Prime Steakhouse in Key West
, just upstairs from Dante’s. Great steaks, the freshest seafood and fine wine selection.
